title: Urban Meyer News, the Rams Roller Coaster, and Your Mailbag Questions
description:
Nora breaks down the recent news of the Urban Meyer firing. Then she is joined by Kaelen Jones to discuss the highs and lows of the 2021 Rams, make predictions about how their season might end, and answer some of your wildest mailbag questions.
Hosts: Nora Princiotti
Guest: Kaelen Jones
Producer: Devon Manze
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
